&lt;li&gt;Worker Impact and Well Being&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engagement and Quality by Type of Tasks, Projects and Metrics to Strengthen Re-engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build an analytics roadmap aligned with organisational priorities, as per existing reporting mandates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shift from ad-hoc analysis to systematic decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;2. Build and own analytics systems&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design automated monitoring pipelines (SQL, Metabase, backend integration)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop reusable data models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure outputs are scalable and decision-oriented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;3. Bridge SQL and social research thinking&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate research questions into SQL logic and measurable indicators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on worker measurement, noisy data, and integration of disparate data sources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure outputs are technically robust and methodologically sound&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;4. Operate under ambiguity&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Convert vague questions into structured hypotheses and analyses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify key questions for the organisation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;5. Strengthen data architecture&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Tech on schema design and data quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reduce manual data cleaning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;6. Lead cross-functional analytics&lt;/h3&gt;
