&lt;p&gt;This is a high-autonomy, high-impact role designed for someone who thrives in the &quot;chaos&quot; of early-stage discovery.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The ideal candidate would have previously founded a startup or were a member of the core founding team (first 5 employees) of a 0-to-1 venture. You know exactly what it takes to build something out of nothing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re excited about closing complex deals that directly fund dignified work for underserved communities, and want to shape GTM strategy at a mission-driven company, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
